title: Philippine client for mac?
body: Is there any Philippine client for mac? I know Garena but it's not compatible with mac please help me, thank you.

replies.body:
Since Riot doesn't control League of Legends deployment or development in the Phillippines, you'll need to reach out to [Garena player support](https://lol.garena.ph/contentSupport.php) about this. 

Let me know if you have any questions.
